cloudkittyclient/v2/scope.py.message:
I had API validation issues when testing: : two or more values in the same group of exclusion 'scope_selector' .

You need to remove every key that doesn't contain anything from the body before making the request. The following quick-and-dirty implementation worked for me::

empty_keys = []
for k, v in body.items():
    if not v:
        empty_keys.append(k)

for k in empty_keys:
    body.pop(k)

